requests.name: GET unprocessed messages within the last month
requests.description:
GET unprocessed TIS messages ('N's) - will only look at the last month
(Used by cdsMonitorApp)-
* typeNid - the type nid of the messsage (optional)
* offsetHours - the number of hours offset from current date/time (required) i.e. the start date for the query
* maxMonths - the number of months to look back (defaults to 1) i.e. the end date
* count - the maximum number of records returned (defaults to 500)
* verbose
